Math Sprint Game

This game highlight the usage of timing events as well as procedurally generating random correct & incorrect Math equations.

Instructions

- You have to select amount of questions to start and choose correct or incorrect answer
- The equations automatically scroll down to the next one as you select the answer
- The timer will stop when you select the last answer and take you to the score page
- You have 0.5s penality score for every incorrect answer
- Your best score is store in LocalStorage

Live Preview Link

https://mathsprintgamesite.netlify.app/
